TOURNIFY
It is a desktop based application. Which  will be very useful for various sport organisations and sport clubs. It will also help schools and colleges to manage their tournaments .It provides a single platform for all the details and management of tournaments and will allow multiple tournament registration, automatic or manual match scheduling and keep the data of all the players and teams together.

BUILT WITH
JDK 14
Java swing
Java AWT

